PROPER_NOUN_DESCRIPTION.Farm-to-Market Road 2050: a road near the wind farm and various ranches
PROPER_NOUN_DESCRIPTION.Mills Bennett Road: a dirt road intersecting Farm-to-Market Road 2050
PROPER_NOUN_DESCRIPTION.San Pablo Road: a road south of the wind farm, extending to the east off Farm-to-Market Road 2050
PROPER_NOUN_DESCRIPTION.Santo Nino Road: also known as Dinn Ranch, extends to the east and provides vehicle access to Highway 16
PROPER_NOUN_DESCRIPTION.Dinn Ranch: also known as Santo Nino Road, extends to the east and provides vehicle access to Highway 16
PROPER_NOUN_DESCRIPTION.Highway 16: a highway providing vehicle access from San Pablo Road and Santo Nino Road
